name: Memorie #2
description:
Caracas has spaces that overwhelm with their mystery, danger, neglect and beauty, Central Park, is one of those.

Its abandonment is only equivalent to the nostalgia it gives when walking through its spaces, missing places that I never got to know.

Second image of collection #1 of "What you remember no longer exists", a sample, from my vision, of those details of my city.
